<small><small style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"><font style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;" size="2"><small><small><br>
  </small></small></font></small><span style="font-style: italic; font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-weight: bold;">2010 September 19 - 22</span><span style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;&nbsp; Tsuboi Sensei seminar (organized by FFA, PAPA, and
 Aikido Philippines)</span><br style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"><br><span style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-style: italic;">(Please note that the seminar venues schedule has been changed slightly, 
as of September 14. The downloadable PDF below reflects this schedule 
change. - 2010 Sept. 14)</span></small><br style="font-style: italic;"><small><br style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">Takeki
Tsuboi Sensei, 7th dan Aikikai, will conduct a seminar in Manila on
2010 September 19 - 22, and will visit Cebu City from September 24 -
25. He will be accompanied by a group of his senior students from
Gessoji Dojo in Japan.</span><br style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">This seminar is a joint project of FFA, PAPA, and Aikido Philippines.</span><br style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">Click
on the link below to download the PDFs of the announcement poster and
the official schedule. You'll need a PDF reader like Adobe Acrobat or
Foxit Reader (both free apps are downloadable from the web).</span></small><br><br><small><a href="tsuboi_poster_v1_3.pdf"><span style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">Tsuboi seminar announcement poster</span></a><br style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"></span><a href="Tsuboi%20Sensei%20Final%20Schedule%2015%20August.pdf"><span style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"></span></a><a href="TsuboiSenseiFinalSchedule15August.pdf"><span style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"></span></a><br><span style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">Click </span><span style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"><a href="../photos/2010_September_19_-_22___Tsuboi_Sensei_seminar_%28organized_by_FFA,_PAPA,_and_Aikido_Philippines%29/index.htm">here</a> </span><span style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">for photo</span></small>.<br style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"><small><span style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"></span><br style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"></small><br><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"></span></font><br><p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font color="#3300cc" face="Arial,Helvetica,Univers,Zurich BT" size="-1"><span style="color: white;">*************************************************************************************************************</span></font></p></td></tr><tr><td style="white-space: nowrap; vertical-align: top;"></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table>&nbsp;
